data.description: Beautiful large home in the quiet county setting of Plain City! This home has updated bathrooms with upgraded flooring in bathrooms and laundry room. Gas fireplace and wood burning stove. Over half acre property with mature trees, beautiful garden area and large pole barn ready for animals. Watch the bald eagles from your windows. Huge two bay detached shop with office and heat. So much to love about this home, come see today!
